metadata.name: Whore of the Metaverse
metadata.description:
They don't only need your body. They want your soul, your dreams and your personality with it. When they get it, the transformation completes.


Animation: x6high

His focus was to complement the electrifying aura and music of this wild composition with his animation decisions.


Music: Can Artsan

The track is a specially made remix of the Synthwave-Darksynth piece 'Excess Madness' from Non-Fungible Albums project.
